---
title: StoreOS Architecture
---
flowchart TD
    A([Customer Message\nEmail / WhatsApp / DM]) --> B

    subgraph PIPELINE ["⚡ StoreOS Autopilot Pipeline"]
        B[/API: /api/classify/] -->|qwen-max| C{Intent\nClassified}
        C --> D[/API: /api/embed/]
        D -->|text-embedding-v4| E[(Customer Context\nOrder History)]
        E --> F[/API: /api/think/]
        F -->|qwen3-235b-thinking| G{Risk\nAssessment}
    end

    G -->|Low Risk| H([Auto-Resolve\nSend Response])
    G -->|High Risk| I([Human Checkpoint\nApproval Queue])

    I -->|Approve| J([Final Response\nqwen-max polishes])
    I -->|Reject| K([Escalate / Modify])

    subgraph VISION ["📦 Product Listing Pipeline"]
        L([Product Photo]) --> M[/API: /api/vision/]
        M -->|qwen-omni-turbo| N([Generated Listing\nTitle · Price · Tags])
    end

    subgraph AUDIT ["📋 Audit Trail"]
        H --> O[(Decision Log)]
        J --> O
        K --> O
    end

    subgraph INFRA ["☁️ Alibaba Cloud"]
        P[Alibaba Cloud OSS\nFile Storage]
        Q[Function Compute\nServerless API]
    end

    style PIPELINE fill:#0f0f1a,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:1px,color:#e8e8e8
    style VISION fill:#0f0f1a,stroke:#8b5cf6,stroke-width:1px,color:#e8e8e8
    style AUDIT fill:#0f0f1a,stroke:#22c55e,stroke-width:1px,color:#e8e8e8
    style INFRA fill:#0f0f1a,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:1px,color:#e8e8e8
